{"tid":458463,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇亞雷斯球荒持續, 射門轉化率只剩5%!!!!","createTime":"2017-11-05T01:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T14:12:00.000Z","uid":34571,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"efc4dc02e902a7c90f7eb41609c219bf80ac1eea","tid":458463,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"事實上今季是蘇亞雷斯同期射門次數最多的，加上對西維爾的比賽，他總共有55腳射門，其中19射正門框範圍，然而只攻入了3球。也就是說，他只有5%的射門轉化為了入球。在今季的西甲聯賽中，C.朗拿度六場比賽射門40次，場均打門6.7次，但是僅攻入1個入球，射門轉化入球率僅為2.5%，這一數字在五大聯賽中墊底。蘇亞雷斯比C.朗拿度稍好，但也一樣不能令人滿意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20171105/8089060/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsoccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2F1%2F20171105%2F8089060%2F&d=7KkDAQFqj8%2BYkqHEThfTyROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=768ea1a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20171105/8089060/</a>"},{"pid":"a4fcceee2e85b3691cc1e11e94fc8ebc0a90ed79","tid":458463,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T01:32:48.000Z","msg":"2cron"},{"pid":"404ef8e02955323ea2877e9fda506a4abff6dac9","tid":458463,"uid":155079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T01:33:27.000Z","msg":"都高過牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0681a399369779a56de0fd3df3f7feae4892bb75","tid":458463,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T01:57:45.000Z","msg":"返利記幫下佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b0e22651987f9cdfd7a24f4026d408967c7175","tid":458463,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T02:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8148d882ec4aa06150d6ea8650dcff114b45f3","tid":458463,"uid":143284,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T02:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img 